4 renewals, or amendments, entered into by any person or firm with the
5 State of Oklahoma shall include a statement certifying that no
6 person who has been involved in any manner in the development,
7 approval, or negotiation of such contract while employed by the
8 state shall be employed or given anything of value to fulfill any of
9 the services provided for under the contract. Each contract,
